{"tid":1934782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港大爆發， 每日雙位數， 就做到經濟攬炒效果， 連登仔敢唔敢？","createTime":"2020-03-20T07:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T16:36:26.000Z","uid":11454,"like":57,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"956ba0c73c054103293bee7de022f3d48eff4e11","tid":1934782,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:00:33.000Z","msg":"唔敢<br />\n香港人，口頭講要攬炒， 又要想無痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明經濟全面崩潰， 先最有效影響港共政權<br />\n最能夠重點打擊，比起上前食TG, 裝修， 聯署乜乜柒柒， 效果之大亦都係九個月街頭抗爭做唔到<br />\n<br />\n文匯都吹風要全面封閉， 非港人唔準入<br />\n（記唔記得毛語錄講乜？）<br />\n<br />\n為求自保， 1月，2月已經錯過第一波爆發機會<br />\n成日話捉到春袋， 依家個春袋喂到埋口<br />\n今次睇下有冇「攬炒」覺悟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c089e5310b3ce8eaa5e75cc08b4dd9e9c171417","tid":1934782,"uid":11454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"口頭攬炒萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67941bce28a13f7202be4350476eb4391f0132c1","tid":1934782,"uid":143621,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:02:41.000Z","msg":"敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c64b6323e093fb256ee19dcef81914119cb6ff","tid":1934782,"uid":132128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:02:49.000Z","msg":"今次真攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2503cd3989c822ff5be8b61991a6fde23c0e0374","tid":1934782,"uid":282435,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"其實後生仔死亡率好低<br />\n<br />\n真係可以神風式攬炒<br />\n<br />\n死亡率低過做火魔 勇武"},{"pid":"077a2088c6288a4ed739369b86c05eef5611452e","tid":1934782,"uid":35087,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:03:36.000Z","msg":"攬中國呀..."},{"pid":"c363994b932896b74dc82517e9a8b543b0aa04c0","tid":1934782,"uid":20272,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0